{"id":488477,"date":[{"year":1968,"month":2,"day":22}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"(锣鼓快板)","count":"501","ytitle":"","mtitle":"万众一心齐动手　(锣鼓快板)","ftitle":"","authors":["陈富森"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"金山县吕巷公社　陈富森"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼口号出场:万众一心，大闹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春耕，搞好生产，分秒必争。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(唱)锣鼓响，红旗飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命形势无限好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓革命，促生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掀起春耕生产新高潮。(锣鼓)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(唱)万众一心齐动手，齐动手呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"齐动手呀齐动手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚决打响——春耕生产第一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮。(锣鼓)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快板:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(一)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级革命派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大闹春耕立新劳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"备战、备荒、为人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席教导永记牢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不失时机闹春耕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“定局”思想要破掉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农业是基础，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮食是宝中宝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓革命，促生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚决打响春耕生产第一炮。(锣鼓)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(二)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫下中农觉悟高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排除万难争分秒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“小熟不好大熟补”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这种论调要破掉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干部群众共商量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团结一致心一条。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女老少齐出动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动干劲冲云霄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习愚公移山志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢教日月换新貌。(锣鼓)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(三)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产队干部挺起腰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大胆领导很重要，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗私批修闹革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产工作抓得牢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间管理不放松，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春耕计划落实早，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兴修水利及时抓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开河积肥掀高潮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千军万马齐上阵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打响春耕生产第一炮。(锣鼓)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(四)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红卫兵小将闹春耕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"意气风发斗志高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化革命做闯将，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大搞春耕逞英豪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步步紧跟毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最新指示落实好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席挥手我前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚决照办不动摇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓革命，促生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打响春耕生产第一炮。(锣鼓)"}]}